snippet.title: Boomerang Jack - Combat Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out our new combat-focused Demo 2.0 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2010010/Boomerang_Jack/

Boomerang Jack is an action-adventure RPG with kinetic free-flow combat. String together boomerang attacks with fast-paced platforming, telekinetic tornadoes and upgradeable powers to unravel a storied, evolving world.

Master arena-style fights against a spread of formidable foes on and achieve an SSS rank.

Beat the devs: Our record is S rank on Insane difficulty. Can you get an SS or SSS?
